Pidcock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It follows up success on the opening day, where Team GB won a bronze and silver - their first opening day medals since 2004.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1291703447506686e-13, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles is also beaten on the floor as she's forced to settle for silver.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She still ends the Paris Games with four medals (of which three are golds), taking her career total to 11 overall.\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An epic comeback after her miserable Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ashock in the balance beam finalas Simone Biles falls and her performance sees her finish fifth.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a slow day for Team GB so far - Molly Caudery and Holly Bradshaw failed to qualify for the pole vault.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\", \"score\": 0.996088676781755, \"rank\": 0.003926664364203432, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource